snippet.title: The Director's Disorder: Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The Director, a psycho killer, has chosen you to play the main character in his next film. Will you play your part and survive the night or will you be his latest victim? 
Coming out for free 1/19/2023 on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2073640/The_Directors_Disorder_Pilot_Episode/
